<item>
 <title>Jessie Street Discusses her Report with McLeod</title>
 <link>https://pilbarastrike.org/content/jessie-street-discusses-her-report-mcleod</link>
 <description>&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-source-file field--type-file field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Source File-PDF:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;file&quot;&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;file-icon&quot; alt=&quot;PDF icon&quot; title=&quot;application/pdf&quot; src=&quot;/modules/file/icons/application-pdf.png&quot; /&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://pilbarastrike.org/sites/default/files/Street-to-McLeod-4-July-1957.pdf&quot; type=&quot;application/pdf; length=484268&quot;&gt;Street-to-McLeod-4-July-1957.pdf&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-source-transcript field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Source Transcript:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Jessie Street to Don McLeod, 4 July 1957, Jessie Street Papers, National Library of Australia, MS 2683/10/334&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On the plane&lt;br /&gt;
Alice Springs to Adelaide&lt;br /&gt;
4.7.57&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Dear Mr McLeod&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Your letter of June 12th caught me up yesterday. I have been out visiting stations &amp;amp; missions &amp;amp; so my letters accumulated at Alice Springs.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;About publishing my report, I would like to send a copy to Mr. Anderson and Mr. Hasluck before it is published &amp;amp; also make a few alterations or clarifications. * I have not had anyone to do any copies and only have one with me which I have shown to a number of people who are all very interested in it but the questions they ask show it needs clarifying. I will do this as soon as I return to Sydney — about 7th and airmail you a copy. I don’t mind you showing the copy you have to anybody.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please let me know &lt;em&gt;fully&lt;/em&gt; what Mr. Jenkinson said. I will be going to Canberra as soon as I have completed my full report &amp;amp; I may be able to help you there. The C’th Social Services should surely be available as a right.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I hope your people at Port Hedland received the photographs I sent them. Please remember me to them &amp;amp; say that my few days at their camps are among my most memorable experiences.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With best wishes for your [success?]&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Jessie M.G. Street&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Have you &amp;amp; Mr. Hughes &amp;amp; Mr Rodereda seen the Minister yet about Yandeyarra?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;* I also want to send a report to Mr Humphrey at the same time of my impressions of all the missions and reserves he arranged for me to see.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-source-citation field--type-text-long field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Source Citation:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Jessie Street to Don McLeod, 4 July 1957, Jessie Street Papers, National Library of Australia, MS 2683/10/334.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-source-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Source Thumbnail:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;img typeof=&quot;foaf:Image&quot; src=&quot;https://pilbarastrike.org/sites/default/files/Street-to-McLeod-4-July-1957-thumbnail.jpg&quot; width=&quot;250&quot; height=&quot;250&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-source-type field--type-taxonomy-term-reference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Source Type:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/source-type/letter&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;Letter&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-source-date- field--type-taxonomy-term-reference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Source Date (for sorting):&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/date/1950-1959&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;1950-1959&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field field--name-field-source-exhibit field--type-taxonomy-term-reference field--label-above&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__label&quot;&gt;Source Exhibit:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__items&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;field__item even&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/exhibits/anti-slavery-society&quot; typeof=&quot;skos:Concept&quot; property=&quot;rdfs:label skos:prefLabel&quot; datatype=&quot;&quot;&gt;The Anti-Slavery Society&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
